{"tid":2099433,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超再現神球！他，曾是被眾人嫌棄的傷兵...","createTime":"2020-07-08T08:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T17:14:20.000Z","uid":122167,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ff83f4e94b018fe530a795d8a9303917600ac0dc","tid":2099433,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"英超護級大戰，屈福特2-1擊敗了諾域治，拿下了關鍵3分。為屈福特攻入制勝球的是韋碧克（Daniel Welbeck），對大多數球迷而言，這是一個已經被遺忘太久的名字了。<br />\n<br />\n韋碧克的入球出現在比賽的第55分鐘，屈福特發動反擊，沙亞（Ismaila Sarr）禁區右路橫傳，皮球擊中防守球員後彈到空中，中路跟進的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">韋碧克二話不說，直接淩空倒掛鳩勾射門</span></strong>，洞穿了諾域治的大門。這個關鍵入球也位屈福特爭取到了寶貴的三分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otB7ZiH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotB7ZiH.gif&h=e5ef978b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3c9566e87f49369fa5e52b5ae01a102cbf19c91","tid":2099433,"uid":33456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"韋大帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2d4277d0eba4f134575e9e62a92ae97983a9c0","tid":2099433,"uid":122167,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我韋碧克降臨!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"978dbe0bea680bf42120cba11ad7381f4641ed2f","tid":2099433,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:38:21.000Z","msg":"宜家嘅佢再同宜家嘅rooney 1 on 1, <br />\n邊個會贏"},{"pid":"9cb61badbababb16565fca10603b56c7a90290a5","tid":2099433,"uid":82889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"